NetworkInfo::Discovery::Nmap
============================

DESCRIPTION

    This module is an extension to NetworkInfo::Discovery which uses the 
    nmap(1) utility to scan networks, find active hosts, their services 
    and operating system. 


INSTALLATION

    To install this module, run the following commands:

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

    Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the 
    following commands:

        perl Build.PL
        ./Build
        ./Build test
        ./Build install


